{"tid":1392126,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"「勵志」「有圖」逆流大叔 - 未來抗爭方向！","createTime":"2019-07-31T15:45:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T16:08:39.000Z","uid":54591,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"73d0dd857574d1a6587af38225b1d1bfeeaebe78","tid":1392126,"uid":54591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T15:45:06.000Z","msg":"原諒小弟因為今日想休息下，唔睇新聞、tg，所以走去睇左套戲: 逆流大叔。當中有幾幕好貼切形容緊香港既一情況。<br />\n<br />\n話説當中因為電訊公司裁員，由吳鎮宇飾演既&rdquo;陳龍&rdquo;就跟大隊番去示威、支持罷工：「罷佢老尾！」但最尾因為淆底，得好少人到場支持，公司最後炒左幾個有份示威既人了事。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kcKPGXK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkcKPGXK.png&h=a0ab5144&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/12owVhL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F12owVhL.png&h=d983f778&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u9bRVhM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu9bRVhM.png&h=c39112d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n陳龍之後因為入左公司搞既龍舟隊而同佢上司王德斌飾演既&rdquo;泰哥&rdquo;熟左。搞搞下龍舟隊又取消左，轉頭又裁員。今次泰哥意識到問題根源係因為班仆街高層炒燶股票而要下層揹，決定發起大罷工。不過今次一罷，就要成個工程部罷工，要斷公司半臂！泰哥自己比錢，自組龍舟隊，最後真係成個工程部罷工。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">我想講既係，只要有一啲掌握經濟命脈既行業大罷工，就可以癱瘓政府！當然好很難，而影響住各大行業有冇得正常返工既就係MTR，<strong>如果MTR各線有多過30名車長帶頭罷工，必定引起連鎖效應！各行各業必定響應罷工，連同不合作運動，車隊慢駛，番工撚想番工都難！(其實729已經見到效果)</strong></span></span><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">影響經濟！資金會外流！呢個係政商、既得利益者最驚既野！</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">既然聽到發夢小朋友缺乏物資，香港人即刻瘋狂掃飯券，裝備。香港人咁有錢，資援工會，令到車長無憂咁罷工有冇得諗呢？</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3TLCQTP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3TLCQTP.png&h=602a0b1b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eTyACyQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeTyACyQ.png&h=f74a475a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gnqn10v.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fgnqn10v.png&h=4b548ea7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ndntXzk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FndntXzk.png&h=6c787bda&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢地跟住自發參賽，但最後關頭有幾個同事因為淆底而退出返去番工，跟住佢地隊就打少個，最後搵個𡃁妹頂上，拎左等三。[size=5]<span style=\"color: red;\">最後！唔該香港人爭氣啲！香港唔應該只為錢！齊心小小！8月5號大罷工！</span>[/size=4]<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">罷佢老尾！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JwgRVow.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJwgRVow.png&h=91772ae1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L68H13w.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL68H13w.png&h=ac45dd20&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ir9W6vb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fir9W6vb.png&h=7c9f2eb4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3AewaWR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3AewaWR.png&h=c7727ea5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3d335ed7b28a705ef7881d6db63cfb375c140a07","tid":1392126,"uid":64131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T16:08:39.000Z","msg":"香港人最緊要有得賴姐<br />\n如果黎多場山竹規模既交通系統breakdown<br />\n咁就算藍絲都被動參與埋罷工"}]}